Dorothy Gulliver https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Gulliver 0 Dorothy Kathleen Gulliver (September 6, 1908 – May 23, 1997) was an American silent film actress, and one of the few to make a successful transition with the advent of "talkies", when films began using sound.
